title: Researchers identify potential new leukemia drug target (The Rockefeller University)
text: ( Source : The Rockefeller University ) New treatment options are badly needed for acute myeloid leukemia, a relatively rare form of cancer. The malignancy begins in the bone marrow, and from there can spread rapidly to the bloodstream,
